result.name: Starbucks

reviews.text:
Seriously bad service. Fully understand how busy . Even cannot entertain request simple one ..dirty tables ..no one clean up..
Simply the worst

I stay here for a drink every weekend. The staff are nice and the food and drinks here are fine. I just hate it how people leave their trash on the tables, making the place dirty and messy and the thing is - no one, not even the staff clean it up.

The barista named Elise is ill-mannered. I missed my drink when I was trying to look for a space to sit down. I returned to the pick up counter about 1 min later and asked my drink politely. Her colleague asked her about if she had already made the drink. She immediately replied “I called it out. No one replied. What can I do?” Well... I wouldn’t expect hearing this kind of conversation when the customer is still standing right in front of you. That’s pretty rude!!
A nice place to chill after going to Buddha and doing some shopping at City Gate
Good place to rest use the close bathrooms in the mall plan and get ready to go on the cable cars. Inside and outside seats.

reviews.text: 在東薈城Starbucks 買了一杯飲品，是新出的士多啤梨沙冰。 士多啤梨肉很豐富，而且滿滿的忌廉，還有粉紅少女心的沙冰。味道不太甜，冰凍得很，很適合夏天喝。店子地方很大，就是服務員很忙，沒有人把桌子收拾。
